channel.title: Need a dedicated team!(RSPS)
channel.description:
Hello! I'm looking for some people to start a RuneScape Private Server with. In the past I have ran some on my own but they had little to no success. Having some sort of team with developers and dedicated moderators would be something to look forward to.
Here is a list of people I'm looking for:
[u][b]Administrators[/b][/u] - Manager [Open] - Advertising [Open] - Developers(2) [Open] - Forums Master [Open] - Economy Management [Open] - Player Support [Open]
Please be no younger than 16!
